Welll... An extremely stupid thing to do, specially since I have all my boring classes tomorrow(math, band, crosstraining, french) but Im going to attempt to stay up the whole night. I came to this decision like just a minute ago when I was eating an apple with peanut butter on it. In like fourty-ish minutes a new Foamy (www.illwillpress.com <----Watch and learn about foamy) cartoon is comin out but after that I have no idea what Ima do.. prolly work on my story I have not yet started x.x;;; Yeah Im just gonna add people at the random and just slaughter everyones personality cause thats just fun. My english homework is sooo evil. Specially since Im a pretty shy person. First nights homework: Say hi to not one person but three people. These three people have to be people you DO NOT know. Which is certainly awkward. Then you have to write down their reactions. Ive got two done, I need one more to do. Second nights: 1.) Make eye contact with someone you DO NOT know for an uncomfortable amount of time. then record their reactions. I havent done it yet.... (yes I know, Im a slacker) 2.) React differently when a friend says hi. Like if you immediatly say hi back and get into a friendly convo, you have to like ignore them er somethin. Then Record their reactions again. Did it, it was hard though cause the whole time I was trying not to laugh but meh.... Third night: Get a lil steno pad thingydingy and observe a group of people for 30mins and see how they interact. I is choosing the magic corner people cause the punk group thing is just so unfun and unspontaneous. Cassy is observing the people that actually play magic. Tis due Monday and it should be interesting. I forgot Skillas phone # today(yes Im such a good friend arent I? :P) but its in my phone... During band we locked Dustyn in one of the band lockers which was okay, he was quiet, specially when Harris came in with no clue of Dustyn even being at school or even in one of the lockers. He went back out of the room and Tory, stupidly, let him out. Then Taren wanted to go in there so they used Kristinas combo lock and locked Taren in there. Then switched to Dustyns key lock and left her in there till Harris came back. He was too distracted to even care that Taren was in there. Basically we did whatever while they got set back up and only actually played music for about fifteen minutes. Now Im just randomly rambling... I once had a dream where I was in Japan in this underground organization with a bowling alley and everything and I went in this one room and came out of a dressing room in Gottschalks and this lady got really mad at me. I also had another dream where my mom left at like 7:22pm and said shed be back at eight and I could drive the beat up black subaru(we dont actually own one but in my dream..) up the hill to Zacks if I wanted. Well then(same dream) we went to Cal Worthingtons and I bought this supposed exotic kitten there. While laying on my bed the kitten turned into a loaf of bread and it was half eaten(hey bread is good) and I even knew that they turned kittens into loaves of bread(dream logic is very odd non?) Yeah Ive decided, there is no one online and Ive still got twenty mins till Foamy comes on so Imma go to sleep for like I dunno, six seven hours tonight? Yeah k well Im going to go because this has gotta be one of the longest entries Ive typed so far(sad isnt it?) See ya ~Megan (btw, awesome free music downloading site: www.aresgalaxy.org and every song works, trust me I use it)

Today was an okay day, woke up went to school and stole Zacks guitar pick. Then I was playing with it in first hour and Peter got really mad at me :P This morning down in the magic corner lowell was there and zack kept wanting me to go down there and say hi but you know... lowell kinda scares me.... sometime during breakfast break Jacob(my friend who went to the carribean) gave me a thing of shells and a bracelet and gave me to give to my mom a pretty big shell with a scorpion on it that said scorpio(cause shes a scorpio) which was cool. Im just now playing with the shells and I think theyre pretty neat. Anyways, now my room smells like guinea pigs cause I have two in there.. nee.. -needs like febreeze er w/e- anyways I should prolly go call Skilla who ish in AL cause she had to go and MOVE. grr well see yall

~Megan

Your inner soul is very mellow. You're very laid
back and pretty much enjoy life! You're quite
an average person, you enjoy hanging out with
your friends, but also making sure you're doing
alright in school. You love to have fun and
laugh, but you're also quiet at times and just
like to soak in the pleasurement of simple
things. You have a pretty good life going on
and wouldn't trade it for anything else :)

What Is Your Inner Soul Trying To Say?
brought to you by Quizilla
In your eyes, people see shards of ice
everywhere... You are cold and distant, pushing
away people that love you and truely care for
you! You want to be able to reach out and love
them but... You can't for some reason... You're
just too.... You :P Underneath that cold
exterior lies a warm, happy soul that wants to
let loose and have fun! Your sanctuary would
probably be anywhere up high where you can look
down on life below you, like the roof of an
apartment building... Your eyes resemble a
saddened, crestfallen person seeking out
attention, but doesn't know how to handle it.
However, you do find comfort from your friends,
they're always there for you, and they know the
REAL you :) Even though you do seem rather
cold, you can be very protective over something
you truely believe in or love. Let go of that
"tough" rep and just be you! It's
impossible to live life without some fun and
love ^-^

What Lies Behind Your Eyes?
brought to you by Quizilla
The one passion that deeply burns in your soul is
longing for love... You're often depressed and
you've been hurt so many times that you tears
seem meaningless, if you even have any left to
cry! You want to be able to reach out and tell
someone everything, making your troubles go
away... But... You jsut can't bring yourself to
do so... Everyday you wish that all of the pain
will just go away... Just disappear... However,
it just seems to get worse and you try to
bottle everything up inside as best as you can!
However, your plan sometimes fails, making you
lash out or break down emotionally. You just
wish to be like everyone else... You want to be
able to tell someone all of your problems...
But you're afraid of admitting your weakness...
You're that outside, loner, mistunderstood
person that has been pushed out of everyones'
life. You desperately try to break through the
barrier, but you guts tell you no... You'll
just be hurt again and again... So why bother?
Your sanctuary is your room, where you can hide
out and be out of 'their' visions. You like to
express your thoughts and feelings through
various forms of art, and try ridding of your
pain in 'different ways.' You're so busy caught
up in your own little, lost world, that you
have yet to realize that a light burns inside
of the darkness of the pack. You might not know
it, but out there... Someone is watching your
every move... Enjoying your presence...
Enjoying you for who YOU are! Wipe away those
tears and open up those beautiful eyes, see the
light! See what you're missing and grasp ahold,
break out of that crust, and mold... Smile your
way through life because the most beautiful
things cannot be concealed forever :)

You know what would be so easy? If you just moved.. I mean, you can sever all ties that way, and not see them again so it wouldnt be awkward. Of course youd be killing yourself at the same time but youd learn not to let people get so close to you next time, in the next town.... Im not trying to leave my friends, I love them lots and would hate to lose them. But at my house, my thoughts become incomplete, depressed thoughts which I have to either try to piece together in my head, or write or type them down. Im not like I am at school because I have my friends to cheer me up, if even just one is hyper or happy, my mood just mirrors that, I dont know why but its kinda cool because I dont like showing my emotions so people wont worry or think Im just an attention seeker. I dont really like a lot of attention really, Im actually kind of shy.. Well I believe thats enough babbling for one day.... bye....
